message.body: Mary my dear! So sorry I missed your call and haven't gotten back to you yet! Will you be around tonight?
Faye!! Hi nooo worries...I should be around tonight. Can't wait to catch up!
Hi Faye!! Sorry I drove back to Dickinson last night and I was so tired I fell asleep super early. Lets try again tonight?? I will be free after work!
No worries!! Sounds perfect, I'll give you a call around 6! Yayy!
Hi love, I'm going to get some take out then call you soon!
Hi! Ok yeah sounds good I'm going to grab food too!
